            <h1>
        TITLE 6</h1>
            <h3>Commerce and Trade</h3>
            <h2>
        SUBTITLE II</h2>
            <h3>Other Laws Relating to Commerce and Trade</h3>
            <h3>
        CHAPTER 27. Contracts</h3>
            <h4>
          Subchapter I. General Provisions</h4>
          </div>
          <div id="CodeBody">
            <div class="Section">
              <div class="SectionHead" id="2701">
          Â§
        2701. Joint and several contracts.</div>
              <p class="subsection">An obligation or written contract of several persons shall be joint and several, unless otherwise expressed.</p>Code 1852,
                Â§
              â1170;Â 
      Code 1915,
                Â§
              â2628;Â 
      Code 1935,
